{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-051", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 51.1", "sort_key": "051.001", "text_original": "道生之，德畜之，物形之，勢成之。", "text_normalized": "道生之，德畜之，物形之，勢成之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-051", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 51.2", "sort_key": "051.002", "text_original": "是以萬物莫不尊道而貴德。", "text_normalized": "是以萬物莫不尊道而貴德。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-051", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 51.3", "sort_key": "051.003", "text_original": "道之尊，德之貴，夫莫之命而常自然。", "text_normalized": "道之尊，德之貴，夫莫之命而常自然。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-051", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 51.4", "sort_key": "051.004", "text_original": "故道生之，德畜之。長之育之，亭之毒之，蓋之覆之。", "text_normalized": "故道生之，德畜之。長之育之，亭之毒之，蓋之覆之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-051", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 51.5", "sort_key": "051.005", "text_original": "生而不有，為而不恃，", "text_normalized": "生而不有，為而不恃，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-006", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-051", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-051__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "老子 51.6", "sort_key": "051.006", "text_original": "長而不宰。是謂玄德。", "text_normalized": "長而不宰。是謂玄德。", "notes": ""}
